posts.description:
Had a wonderful birthday today 😍 Firstly I spent it in my favourite city in the world (other than singapore): Tokyo. Then I spent it doing one of my favourite things in the world: Filming for Guide To Life!!! 😎 Plus it's extra special because the day I turn 33 was spent filming for the 200th episode of Guide to Life, and we spent 24hrs awake to chat and interact with all our most loyal viewers!! 😌😌😌 It was so so so fun and I'm so glad I got to speak with the whole lot of you especially Icarus, Go go, missamik, Fae... and all those I didn't mention who came to watch too. Plus this time you guys can finally meet Gillian and Dan who are behind the scenes of the GTL episodes you watch. The 24hrs is finally over but exhausted as I am I didn't want it to end. 😭
.
Thanks to @samanthathavasa.sg who let me meet their new ambassadors in the Samantha Thavasa flagship store and interview them: @sofiarichie (in pic), @sarahfuckingsnyder, @lottiemossxo and @kenyakinskij!
.
Although I didn't spend my birthday with my family it's ok because in 2 days I'm bringing Dash to @hkdisneyland and Daddy + Popo + Dash recorded me a sweet happy birthday song! 🎈🎂
.
Flying home today and feeling really really loved and very grateful for all that I have in my life 😭 .
And thank you to everyone who sent me birthday wishes!!! Love ya guys!!!! #happy

OILY FACE OR PAINT? 😱😱😱 Swipe left or zoom in to see the truth!! Hahaha!!! Did my optical illlusion trick you? Check out my latest YouTube video where I show you how I did this!! 😊 https://youtu.be/HnxAgTfBjyA or click on my bio!
Yay new Guide to Life is up!!! @clicknetwork go click on their bio if you don't already have the app!

Ok my [Why I Am Not A Feminist video + Dumbest Feminist Quotes] is reuploaded!

Yesterday the video mysteriously was taken down. I don't know what the fuck happened because I sure as hell didn't delete it. 😡 The error message said it is deleted by user but I wasn't hacked or anything?! I really hope it wasn't like taken down because it is too controversial or something. 😳

I lost 20,000 initial views and over 500 comments. Very irritated!! Anyway here it is again so quick watch it just in case it's gone again. 😒

Click on link in bio or go to https://youtu.be/bVspgkYbJl4

Ps: If you have something against women who are not feminist, I suggest you watch the video first before insulting me here. Otherwise you just appear rather misinformed.

UPDATE: THE VIDEO GOT DELETED AND IT SAYS DELETED BY USER WTF?! I don't know what happened, is it just YouTube censoring controversial content? (Actually the video isn't even that controversial) will update you guys when I find out.

New YouTube video is up!! Find out why I'm not a feminist! Ehhhh it was supposed to be out earlier around International Women's Day hahaha... Trigger warning!

Me and my prince hahahaha 💘 I never miss a chance to dress up as a princess!! 👸🏼🤴🏻 Have you guys watched my Beauty and The Beast makeup tutorial yet??? I forced @mikesayre to be in it hahaha!!! Link on my bio or go to http://YouTube.com/xiaxue

Today @clicknetwork got presented with our GOLD PLAY BUTTON, for hitting 1 million YouTube subscribers!!! 😍 I know I've said this so many times but I'm so proud that we all hit this milestone!! Here with Gillian and Rozz, with whom Girls Out Loud: Road Trip came into fruition and launched the first Clicknetwork series. I watched the subscribers go from 0 to 1 million and it's been so wonderful in between... hopefully it will continue to be for a long long time. 😍 love ya Click fam!! Cameo by @oonshuan and @rjt99 hehehe we all get to keep our giant posters!! Thank you Google for hosting such a wonderful party for us!!

I'm so in love with my pink hair!! 🦄🍬🍭🎀💕 I don't know why I didn't go back to pink sooner!!! It's like having cotton candy as hair 😍 Thank you so much @hairbyoliviakoh and @nextthesalonhv for the fantastic dye job as usual! If you guys can't tell, the pink is actually a little ombré, lighter baby pink at the ends 😍 If you want to try some exciting colours, you can go to @hairbyoliviakoh - 30% off for first timers!! Check with her for more details. 😊 Lens by @nobluklens!! Thank you so much @nobluk I love all the colours!!

The sunset at Ku De Ta is just INSANE!! 🌊🌈🌅 Looks like a freaking wallpaper omg!! It's our @clicknetwork team's last day in Bali... at the airport now and can't wait to go home to my puff ❤️ photo: @bubbleriotpants
